back home no matter what.

92
00:11:00,515 --> 00:11:03,815
And that's a promise
of a lifetime.

93
00:11:03,848 --> 00:11:04,948
-Do not worry.

94
00:11:04,982 --> 00:11:08,415
I can finish this one.

95
00:11:08,448 --> 00:11:09,348
