96
00:11:17,748 --> 00:11:19,115
-I don't think so.

97
00:11:25,815 --> 00:11:26,615
-You die!

98
00:11:30,515 --> 00:11:34,115
-I dislike being ignored.

99
00:11:34,148 --> 00:11:34,615
-Ah.

100
00:11:38,582 --> 00:11:41,015
NARUTO (VOICEOVER):
Good luck, bushy brow.

101
00:11:41,048 --> 00:11:42,748
-You can not afford
to be distracted.

102
00:11:46,982 --> 00:11:47,748
(VOICEOVER) Yes!

103
00:11:47,782 --> 00:11:49,582
