104
00:12:10,915 --> 00:12:15,015
-Still, no matter how you look
at it, with Sasuke bottled up

105
00:12:15,048 --> 00:12:18,315
in that coffin, there's not
a team of Genin on earth

106
00:12:18,348 --> 00:12:19,815
that can take on
that bunch and win.

107
00:12:22,448 --> 00:12:24,215
-Obviously the
two of us can't be

108
00:12:24,248 --> 00:12:26,948
of much help in our condition.

109
00:12:26,982 --> 00:12:29,448
