a special squad,

110
00:12:29,482 --> 00:12:32,248
send out a team of
Jonin to back them up--

111
00:12:32,282 --> 00:12:35,582
-That's out of the question.

112
00:12:35,615 --> 00:12:38,215
Ever since Orochimaru's
attack, we've

113
00:12:38,248 --> 00:12:39,915
had to defend
ourselves with merely

114
00:12:39,948 --> 00:12:42,015
a fraction of our
former strength.

115
00:12:42,048 --> 00:12:44,915
Other lands have begn
to sense our weakness.

116
00:12:44,948 --> 00:12:47,348
Every day we're faced
with growing dangers,

117
00:12:47,382 --> 00:12:49,182
both from within
and from without.

118
00:12:54,215 --> 00:12:56,548
Even at the risk of
letting the Sharingan

119
00:12:56,582 --> 00:12:58,382
fall into Orochimaru's hands.

120
00:13:00,948 --> 00:13:05,315
What I need is every Jonin
here to defend the village.

121
00:13:05,348 --> 00:13:09,482
-But, my lady, the
problem of Orochimaru--

122
00:13:09,515 --> 00:13:11,848
well, it won't just go away.

123
00:13:11,882 --> 00:13:16,482
-If he regains his powers,
sooner or later he'll be back.

124
00:13:16,515 --> 00:13:18,615
-Of course he will.

125
00:13:18,648 --> 00:13:20,382
I'm well aware of that.

126
00:13:20,415 --> 00:13:23,315
I'm not a fool.

127
00:13:23,348 --> 00:13:26,448
And that's why I've already
taken certain measures.

128
00:13:29,682 --> 00:13:31,082
Huh?

129
00:13:31,115 --> 00:13:31,815
-She's in here.

130
00:13:41,082 --> 00:13:42,015
TSUNADE: Guy!

131
00:13:42,048 --> 00:13:42,982
What is it?

132
00:13:43,015 --> 00:13:45,282
