on your mission?

133
00:13:45,315 --> 00:13:46,615
-No.

134
00:13:46,648 --> 00:13:47,982
It went without a hitch.

135
00:13:48,015 --> 00:13:52,948
And then I ran back as swiftly
as my feet could carry me.

136
00:13:52,982 --> 00:13:56,048
